===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# Any of various [[species]] of [[flowering plant]] of the [[genus]] ''[[Claytonia]]'', primarily native to the [[Americas]] and [[northeastern]] [[Asia]].
#* '''2010''', Robert Michael Pyle, ''Mariposa Road: The First Butterfly Big Year'' (page 123)
#*: On the lane below, more orangetips nectared on '''spring beauties''' and violets.
# {{lb|en|obsolete}} A small American butterfly, the {{vern|early hairstreak}} ({{taxlink|Erora laeta|species|ver=180618}}), which appears in spring. The hind wings of the male are brown, bordered with deep blue; those of the female are mostly blue.

